          "Handling censored data in prep time estimation",
          "Model drift over time",
          "Overfitting due to reliance on historical patterns"
        ]
      },
      "optimization_layer": {
        "purpose": "To make final dispatch decisions by scoring and ranking potential offers, batching orders, and strategically delaying dispatches when necessary.",
        "tools_used": [
          "Mixed-integer programming (MIP) solver (Gurobi)",
          "Dynamic dispatch engine"
        ],
        "decision_factors": [
          "Efficiency (Dasher time utilization)",
          "Quality (delivery speed and on-time performance)",
          "Batching opportunities",
          "Trade-offs between delivery speed and Dasher earnings"
        ],
        "challenges": [
          "Cascading variability from ML predictions",
          "Overfitting in optimization parameters",
          "Balancing short-term gains with long-term performance"
        ]
      }
    },
    "interactions_between_ml_and_optimization": {
      "challenge_1": {
        "name": "Garbage in, garbage out",
        "description": "If ML models produce inaccurate or outdated predictions (e.g., due to model drift), the optimization layer's decisions will also degrade. This is mitigated by continuous retraining of ML models and using fresh, rolling historical and real-time data."
      },
      "challenge_2": {
        "name": "Overfitting in optimization parameters",
        "description": "Optimization parameters may become overly tuned to historical data, leading to poor performance with new, unseen scenarios. This is addressed using Bayesian optimization techniques to tune parameters adaptively and robustly."
      },
      "challenge_3": {
        "name": "Cascading variability",
        "description": "Each ML model introduces variance into the system, which can accumulate as routes become more complex (e.g., through batching). The scoring function in the optimization layer accounts for this by adding penalty terms for increased complexity."
      }
    },
