      "description": "For each user, we need a set of candidate files to rank. Since Dropbox users could potentially have thousands or even millions of files, it would be very expensive to rank all of them—and not very useful either, since a lot of files are rarely accessed. Instead, we can limit to the most recent files that the user has interacted with, without a significant loss in accuracy.",
