      "description": "This model provides agents with just-in-time guidance based on user conversations. It uses a mastermind QA model to answer intent-specific questions and recommend templates to agents.",
      "key_metrics": [
        "Improved engagement rate in production",
        "Better alignment with CS policy through API and model intent checks"
      ],
      "implementation_details": [
        "Used t5-base and Narrativa as backbone models",
