  "conclusion": "Text generation models have significantly improved Airbnb’s customer support by enabling content recommendation, real-time agent assistance, and chatbot paraphrasing. These models have enhanced user experiences, improved agent efficiency, and demonstrated the potential of text generation in NLP applications."
