    "strategy_summary": "Pinterest's AAL strategy focuses on innovation in audience expansion through advanced machine learning models and scalable infrastructure. The system is designed to handle large-scale data and improve operational efficiency. The strategy also includes future directions like deep modeling and contextual AAL to further enhance audience targeting. The approach aligns with broader goals of improving system efficiency and reducing infrastructure costs."
